    <h2 class="world__title">SIDE QUESTS</h2>

    <div class="cabinets">
      <article class="cabinet pixel-border">
        <h3 class="cabinet__title">AI TRAVEL ITINERARY GENERATOR</h3>
        <p>
          Travel planner that generates personalized day-wise itineraries —
