  <!-- ============ WORLD 5 · DEV LOG ============ -->
  <div class="dots" aria-hidden="true"><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i><i></i></div>
  <section class="world wrap" id="world-5">
    <p class="world__label">WORLD 5</p>
    <h2 class="world__title">DEV LOG</h2>
    <p class="t-muted" style="margin: -14px 0 26px;">
      Field notes from work, side quests, and whatever rabbit hole ate this
      week. Curiosity-driven — the résumé does not get a veto.
